*polkit-gnome-0.96-r1 (11 Aug 2010)

  11 Aug 2010; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  +polkit-gnome-0.96-r1.ebuild:
  Replace OnlyShowIn=GNOME; with NotShowIn=KDE; because polkit-gnome is
  useful also for LXDE, XFCE, and others.

